'''拉米亞航空班機2933號空難'''（LaMia，LMI 2933）是發生於{{tsl|en|Time_in_Colombia|哥倫比亞時間}}2016年11月28日的[[空難|空難]]，機上運載有[[巴西|巴西]][[足球會|足球會]][[查比高恩斯|沙佩科人]]的成員。班機由[[玻利維亞|玻利維亞]][[維魯維魯國際機場|維魯維魯國際機場]]出發，原定于麦德林时间22时45分在位于[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]][[麥德林|麥德林]]的[[何塞·瑪麗亞·科爾多瓦國際機場|何塞·瑪麗亞·科爾多瓦國際機場]]降落。22时15分，由于机长的错误操作，飞机在跑到前方16公里处擦破树林坠毁。事發班機為[[英国宇航系统|英国宇航系统公司]]制造的[[BAe_146|Avro RJ85]]，機上載有77人，包括68名乘客（接載球隊成員和21名記者）和9名機組人員。球會原定抵达哥倫比亞出戰[[2016年南美球會盃|2016南联杯]]決賽，對阵哥伦比亚[[國民體育會_(哥倫比亞)|麦德林国民]]。據報球隊只有3名球員生還，其他球隊成員均已罹難，球賽亦告無限期延後，而國民體育會方面亦已宣佈要求賽會將[[2016年南美球會盃|南联杯]]頒予沙佩科人<ref name="crs">{{cite news|title=Brazil football team Chapocoense in Colombia plane crash|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38140981|accessdate=2016-11-29|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|英國廣播公司新聞]]|date=2016-11-29|archive-date=2016-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130070128/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38140981|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|work=[[國家報|國家報]]|language=es|url=http://internacional.elpais.com/internacional/2016/11/29/america/1480398356_994950.html?id_externo_rsoc=TW_CM|first1=Javier|last1=Lafuente|first2=Ana|last2=Marcos|title=Un avión que transportaba al equipo de fútbol brasileño del Chapecoense sufre un accidente en Colombia|date=2016-11-29|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2016-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201102951/http://internacional.elpais.com/internacional/2016/11/29/america/1480398356_994950.html?id_externo_rsoc=TW_CM|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Plane Carrying Football Players From Brazil Crashes In Colombia|url=http://www.ndtv.com/world-news/plane-carrying-football-players-from-brazil-crashes-in-colombia-1631523?browserpush=true|accessdate=2016-11-29|work=[[新德里電視台|新德里電視台]]|date=2016-11-29|archive-date=2018-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705233052/https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/plane-carrying-football-players-from-brazil-crashes-in-colombia-1631523?browserpush=true|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Plane carrying Brazilian football team Chapecoense crashes in Colombia|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/nov/29/plane-carrying-brazilian-footballers-team-chapecoense-crashes-en-route-to-medellin|accessdate=2016-11-29|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108165104/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/nov/29/plane-carrying-brazilian-footballers-team-chapecoense-crashes-en-route-to-medellin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。機上有6人被救出時仍有生命跡象，但送醫急救後僅有5人生還，1人宣告不治<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.cnn.com/2016/11/29/americas/colombia-plane-accident/index.html | title = Colombia plane crash: 6th survivor found | first1 = Joshua | last1 = Berlinger | first2 = Marilia | last2 = Brocchetto | first3 = Fernando | last3 = Ramos | publisher = [[CNN|CNN]] | access-date = 2016-11-29 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116212442/https://www.cnn.com/2016/11/29/americas/colombia-plane-accident/index.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。事发前因一架[[哥伦比亚愉快航空|哥伦比亚愉快航空]]的飞机由于已经出现漏油，被准予优先降落。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2016/12/161201_chapecoense_crash_airline_suspended |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-04-15 |archive-date=2019-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190623211218/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2016/12/161201_chapecoense_crash_airline_suspended |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==航班==
飞机型号为[[BAe_146|Avro RJ85]]，注册编号CP-2933<ref name=AH>{{cite web|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=4a16583c&opt=0|title=Crash: LAMIA Bolivia RJ85 near Medellin on Nov 28th 2016, electrical problems, impact with terrain|first=Simon|last=Hradecky|work=Aviation Herald|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://archive.today/20161203161047/http://avherald.com/h?article=4a16583c&opt=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[序列号|序列号]]E.2348，于1999年3月26日首飞<ref name=ASN>{{cite web |url=https://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20161128-0 |title=CP-2933 accident description |publisher=Aviation Safety Network |accessdate=2016-11-29 |archive-date=2016-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129143034/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20161128-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[法国航空|法国航空]]名下服役于{{le|美莎巴航空|Mesaba Airlines}}和[[城捷航空|城捷航空]]后，2010年到2013年间停飞，之后被委内瑞拉和玻利维亚合资航空公司[[拉米亚航空|拉米亚航空]]收购<ref name=Planespotters>{{cite web|url=https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/British-Aerospace/BAe-146/E2348/CP-2933-LAMIA|title=CP-2933 LAMIA British Aerospace Avro RJ85 – cn E2348|publisher=Planespotters|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2016-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129152931/https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/British-Aerospace/BAe-146/E2348/CP-2933-LAMIA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事发时，CP-2933是拉米亚航空三架RJ85飞机中唯一在飞的班机<ref name="marca">{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/futbol/america/2016/11/29/583d7c31468aeb04128b4578.html|work=Marca|first=Fabián|last=Torres|title=El piloto del avión siniestrado también era el dueño de la aerolínea LaMia|date=2016-11-29|accessdate=2016-11-29|language=es|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930170110/https://www.marca.com/futbol/america/2016/11/29/583d7c31468aeb04128b4578.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==事故==
机上载有68名乘客和9名机组成员。航班从[[玻利维亚|玻利维亚]][[圣克鲁斯_(玻利维亚)|圣克鲁斯]]飞往[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]][[麦德林|麦德林]]<ref name=CNN>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/11/29/americas/colombia-plane-accident/index.html#|work=CNN|title=Colombia plane crash: 71 dead on Brazil soccer team's charter flight|accessdate=2016-11-30|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116212442/https://www.cnn.com/2016/11/29/americas/colombia-plane-accident/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。部分乘客将参加[[2016年南美球會盃|2016南联杯]]决赛，对阵[[国民竞技|麦德林国民]]。

{{le|巴西国家民航局|National Civil Aviation Agency of Brazil}}拒绝了沙佩科恩斯包机从[[圣保罗|圣保罗]]直飞[[麦德林|麦德林]]的请求，导致圣克鲁斯的航班停飞及变更<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.eltiempo.com/deportes/futbol/equipo-chapecoense-cambio-de-vuelo-por-decision-de-aviacion-brasilena/16761425 |work=El Tiempo |language=es |title=Al Chapecoense lo hicieron cambiar de avión |trans-title=Chapecoense was made to change aircraft |date=2016-11-29 |access-date=2016-11-29 |archive-date=2016-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202082231/http://www.eltiempo.com/deportes/futbol/equipo-chapecoense-cambio-de-vuelo-por-decision-de-aviacion-brasilena/16761425 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。民航局要求包机公司属巴西或哥伦比亚才授权直航，但俱乐部选择了曾载运过其他[[南美洲足球协会|南美洲足球协会]]比赛俱乐部的拉米亚航空<ref name="marca"/>。在18天前，该公司曾用同一架航班运送过[[阿根廷国家足球队|阿根廷国家足球队]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.infobae.com/deportes-2/2016/11/29/messi-y-la-seleccion-argentina-viajaron-en-el-mismo-avion-del-accidente-de-chapecoense-hace-18-dias/|work=Infobae|title=Messi y la Selección argentina viajaron en el mismo avión del accidente hace 18 días|trans-title=Messi and the Argentine team travelled in the accident aircraft 18 days ago|accessdate=2016-11-29|date=2016-11-29|language=es|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020212152/https://www.infobae.com/deportes-2/2016/11/29/messi-y-la-seleccion-argentina-viajaron-en-el-mismo-avion-del-accidente-de-chapecoense-hace-18-dias/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

两座机场相隔{{convert|1605|nmi|km}}，略高于Avro RJ85规定标准范围{{convert|1600|nmi|km|0}}，最大航行距离为{{convert|2600|nmi|km}}，所需油量相当于3个辅助油箱<ref name=Jacdec>{{cite web|url=http://www.jacdec.de/2016/11/29/2016-11-28-lamia-avro-rj-85-crashed-near-medellin-with-81-on-board/|title=2016-11-28 LAMIA Avro RJ-85 crashed near Medellin with 81 on board|first=Jan|last=Richter|publisher=JACDEC|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2016-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206013953/http://www.jacdec.de/2016/11/29/2016-11-28-lamia-avro-rj-85-crashed-near-medellin-with-81-on-board/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[UTC-5|当地时间]]11月28日晚上22点（[[UTC|UTC]]时间11月29日凌晨3点），飞机在哥伦比亚[[拉塞哈|拉塞哈]]和[[拉乌尼翁_(安蒂奥基亚省)|拉乌尼翁]]之间的空域飞行时燃料告急，机组人员发出燃油耗尽紧急警报<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ostrower|first1=John|title=Colombia plane crash: Jet ran out of fuel, pilot said|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/29/americas/colombia-plane-crash-investigation/index.html|accessdate=2016-11-30|agency=CNN|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125023750/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/29/americas/colombia-plane-crash-investigation/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite web|last1=Audio Recording|first1=Controller|title=Pilot:|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7r0NVL3TrwI&t=543|website=LMI 2933 Pilot: (We are) in complete electrical and fuel failure|publisher=Youtube|accessdate=2016-11-30|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305035540/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7r0NVL3TrwI&t=543|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Lanacion">{{cite news|url=http://www.lanacion.com.ar/1960605-accidente-chapecoense-tareas-de-rescate|work=La Nación|title=Accidente de Chapecoense: los rescatistas tienen que subir media hora por la montaña a pie|language=es|date=2016-11-29|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2018-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706103840/https://www.lanacion.com.ar/1960605-accidente-chapecoense-tareas-de-rescate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。飞行最后15分钟，航班以跑道[[等待航线|等待航线]]姿态绕飞两周，飞行距离增加约{{convert|54|nmi|km|0}}。坠机地点距[[何塞·玛丽亚·科尔多瓦国际机场|何塞·玛丽亚·科尔多瓦国际机场]]第36跑道{{convert|10|nmi|km|0}}。

{{le|哥伦比亚空军|Colombian Air Force}}直升机起初因[[大雾|大雾]]无法抵达现场<ref name="AH" />，而事发两小时后救援人员抵达现场时，发现现场有区域散落着直径约{{convert|100|m}}的碎片<ref name="eltiempo"/>。到11月29日凌晨2点，首位生还者、沙佩科恩斯球员{{le|阿兰·卢舍尔|Alan Ruschel}}被送往拉赛贾（{{lang|es|La Ceja}}）医院<ref name="eltiempo">{{cite news|url=http://www.eltiempo.com/colombia/medellin/avion-que-transportaba-a-jugadores-del-chapecoense-se-accidento-en-antioquia/16761383|work=El Tiempo|title=Son seis los sobrevivientes del accidente aéreo en Antioquia|date=2016-11-29|language=es|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2017-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204091441/http://www.eltiempo.com/colombia/medellin/avion-que-transportaba-a-jugadores-del-chapecoense-se-accidento-en-antioquia/16761383|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最初有7人幸存，但首发门将{{le|马科斯·达尼洛·帕蒂尔哈|Marcos Danilo Padilha|达尼洛}}在送院后死亡。最后一名幸存者是球员{{le|内托|Neto (footballer, born 1985)}}，于5点40分被发现<ref name="caracol">{{Cite news|url=http://noticias.caracoltv.com/colombia/avion-que-transportaba-al-equipo-chapecoense-de-brasil-se-encuentra-desaparecido|title=Accidente de avión en el que viajaba Chapecoense deja 75 personas muertas|date=2016-11-29|newspaper=Caracol.tv|language=es|access-date=2016-11-29|archive-date=2016-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130034943/http://noticias.caracoltv.com/colombia/avion-que-transportaba-al-equipo-chapecoense-de-brasil-se-encuentra-desaparecido|dead-url=no}}</ref>。替补门将{{le|贾克森·弗罗曼|Jakson Follmann}}[[截肢|截肢]]后幸存<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/news/2016/11/29/goalie-follmann-leg-amputated-neto-suffering-from-head-trauma/|title=Goalie Follmann's leg amputated, Neto suffering from head trauma|date=2016-11-29|newspaper=Fox News Latino|language=en|access-date=2016-11-30}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。包括达尼洛在内，77名乘客中有71人坠机身亡，死亡人数最初是75人，后据透露有4人未登机<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lawlor|first1=David|title=Colombia plane crash: 71 dead and six survivors on flight carrying Chapecoense football team|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/11/29/colombia-plane-carrying-brazil-football-team-crashes-latest/|accessdate=2016-11-29|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2016-11-29|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622023522/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/11/29/colombia-plane-carrying-brazil-football-team-crashes-latest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

