==调查==
哥伦比亚{{le|民用航空特别行政单位|Special Administrative Unit of Civil Aeronautics}}飞机事故调查组负责调查事故，要求飞机制造商[[英国宇航|英国宇航]]和[[英国航空事故调查局|英国航空事故调查局]]以制造方身份作为调查机构协助调查。调查局派出3人组成的调查队<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.la-razon.com/ciudades/seguridad_ciudadana/Colombia-avion-accidente-Chapecoense_0_2609739060.html|work=La Razón|first=Paulo|last=Cuiza|title=DGAC envía comisión de investigadores a Colombia y asegura que nave de Lamia partió de Bolivia en perfectas condiciones|trans-title=DGAC sends panel of investigators to Colombia and states that the LaMia aircraft left Bolivia in perfect condition|date=2016-11-29|accessdate=2016-11-29|language=es|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130113808/http://www.la-razon.com/ciudades/seguridad_ciudadana/Colombia-avion-accidente-Chapecoense_0_2609739060.html|archive-date=2016-11-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。加入调查的还有{{le|玻利维亚国家航空局|Dirección General de Aeronáutica Civil (Bolivia)}}调查人员<ref name=AAIB>{{cite press release|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/the-aaib-is-sending-a-team-of-inspectors-to-colombia|title=The AAIB is sending a team of inspectors to Colombia|publisher=Air Accidents Investigation Branch|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610231909/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/the-aaib-is-sending-a-team-of-inspectors-to-colombia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

哥伦比亚空军从残骸中搜获70具遇难者遗体，已全部带回基地后送往麦德林医学研究机构进行尸检鉴定<ref>{{cite news|url=http://g1.globo.com/mundo/noticia/corpos-de-vitimas-de-queda-do-voo-da-chapecoense-ja-estao-todos-no-iml-de-medellin.ghtml|work=G1|3=|title=Corpos de vítimas de queda do voo da Chapecoense já estão todos no IML de Medellin|trans-title=Bodies of victims of the Chapecoense air crash are already at the IML in Medellín|date=2016-11-29|accessdate=2016-11-29|language=pt|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617165828/https://g1.globo.com/mundo/noticia/corpos-de-vitimas-de-queda-do-voo-da-chapecoense-ja-estao-todos-no-iml-de-medellin.ghtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在事故中幸存的的乘务员表示，飞机燃料耗尽<ref name=Metro6293649>{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/11/30/final-panicked-words-of-pilot-in-colombian-plane-crash-as-he-ran-out-of-fuel-6293649/ |title=Final panicked words of pilot in Colombian plane crash as he 'ran out of fuel' |first=Richard |last=Hartley-Parkinson |publisher=Associated Newspapers Ltd |work=Metro |accessdate=2016-11-30 |archive-date=2019-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628191705/https://metro.co.uk/2016/11/30/final-panicked-words-of-pilot-in-colombian-plane-crash-as-he-ran-out-of-fuel-6293649/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他乘务员有听到航班飞行员在无线电中报称飞机燃料用完，需要紧急迫降<ref name=Reuters001>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-colombia-crash-idUKKBN13O0DA|title=Soccer crash survivors treated in Colombia as investigation begins|work=Reuters UK|accessdate=2016-11-30|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809151849/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-colombia-crash-idUKKBN13O0DA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而调查队领队表示“没有证据显示飞机因燃料耗尽迫降”，飞机坠毁时没有爆炸<ref name=AH />。事故成因疑是燃料耗尽<ref name=CNN />。

11月29日下午，民用航空特别行政单位表示，两台[[飞行记录仪|飞行记录仪]]完好无损<ref name=AH />。

有报道指出事故原因可能与机组成员在起飞前试图寻找某乘客的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]从而导致起飞延迟有关。起飞延迟使航班没能在午夜关闭时间之前抵达加油机场，错过了本应在中途进行的停降加油。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Steinbuch|first1=Yaron|title=Search for video game may be why Colombia plane didn’t refuel|url=http://nypost.com/2016/12/02/search-for-video-game-may-be-why-colombia-plane-didnt-refuel/|accessdate=2016-12-05|publisher=纽约邮报|date=2016-12-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204170931/http://nypost.com/2016/12/02/search-for-video-game-may-be-why-colombia-plane-didnt-refuel/|archivedate=2016-12-04|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Willoughby|first1=James|title=Chapecoense air disaster: radical crash theory|url=http://thenewdaily.com.au/sport/football/2016/12/02/chapecoense-plane-crash-2/|accessdate=2016-12-05|date=2016-12-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203002752/http://thenewdaily.com.au/sport/football/2016/12/02/chapecoense-plane-crash-2/|archivedate=2016-12-03|language=en}}</ref>

事故發生四周後，調查證實事故的原因是燃料耗盡。航空公司的糟糕規劃以及玻利維亞航空當局監管不力被視為促成因素。初步事故報告指出，飛行員已經討論了他們的燃料狀態以及燃料可能在途中耗盡。由於未知原因，CVR在FDR之前一小時四十分鐘停止錄製。

